presentation
Interface PresentationElement

All Known Implementing Classes:
Edge, EdgeHandler, GraphElement, GraphLabel, LatexLabel, Node, SelectionGroup
public interface PresentationElement

Interface for any object that can appear in the drawing area. Follows Composite (recursive composition) design pattern.

Author:
Helen Bretzke
